@title ExecutionLog
 @notice Canonical ledger of workflow executions attested by validators.
@notice Address empowered to manage validator roster and quorum.
@notice Address permitted to submit batched validator attestations.
@notice Number of validator approvals required to accept an execution.
@notice Metadata for each recorded execution.
@notice Simplified validator approval referenced for auditability.
@notice Records an execution after validator quorum is achieved.
@notice Fetches execution record for downstream modules.
@notice Enables or disables a validator.
@notice Updates quorum requirement.
@notice Updates attestation aggregator.
@notice Transfers governance.

@title HAI Token
 @notice ERC-20 token powering the HavnAI protocol with governance-managed emission.
@notice Mapping that stores account balances.
@notice Mapping that stores allowances granted to spenders.
@notice Total supply of tokens in circulation.
@notice Token metadata name.
@notice Token metadata symbol.
@notice Token decimals as per ERC-20 specification.
@notice Address of contract governance.
@notice Optional emission controller allowed to mint in addition to governance.
@notice Emitted when tokens are moved between accounts.
@notice Emitted when an allowance is granted or updated.
@notice Emitted when the emitter role is updated.
@notice Emitted when governance is transferred.

@param initialGovernance Address that receives governance rights.
 @param initialEmitter Address capable of minting tokens alongside governance.
@notice Returns the total amount of tokens in circulation.
@notice Reads the balance of an account.
@notice Moves tokens from caller to recipient.
@notice Reads allowance from owner to spender.

@notice Mints new tokens to `to`. Callable by governance or emitter.

@notice Updates the emitter role. Governance-only action.
@notice Transfers governance to a new address.

@title PayoutSplitter
 @notice Splits $HAI fees between creators, contributors, validators, and treasury per workflow configuration.
@notice Basis points denominator shared with registry.
@notice Stable reference to $HAI token.
@notice Reference to execution log.
@notice Reference to workflow registry.
@notice Governance controller for treasury and overrides.
@notice Treasury address receiving protocol share.
@notice Tracks whether a job has been settled.
@notice Maps upstream asset identifiers to recipient wallets.

@title StakingManager
 @notice Bonds and slashes stake for HavnAI nodes and validators.

@notice Minimum stake required for node operators.
@notice Minimum stake required for validators.

@notice Slashes stake for misbehavior by sending penalty to recipient.
@notice Updates system parameters.
@notice Transfers governance role.

@title WorkflowRegistry
 @notice Manages workflow manifests, dependency graphs, and royalty splits for the HavnAI protocol.

@notice Describes an upstream dependency receiving royalties.
@notice Input helper for dependency registration.
@notice Registers a new workflow manifest with royalty route and dependencies.
